<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Automaton&action=edit&section=9.php.html" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Bailly, Christian. <i>Automaten</i>, Hirmer</li>
<li>Bailly, Christian (2003). <i>Automata: The Golden Age 1848-1914</i>, Robert Hale, 360pp, <a href="Special_BookSources/0709074034" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-7090-7403-4</a>. Translation of 1991 <i>L'AGE D'OR DES AUTOMATES 1848-1914</i></li>
<li>Beyer, Annette (1983). <i>Faszinierende Welt der Automaten</i>. Callwey Verlag Munchen　</li>
