<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0149-6611(192003)35:3%3C129:TPBAHA%3E2.0.CO;2-%23">M. B. Ogle, 'The Perilous Bridge and Human Automata', <i>Modern Language Notes</i>, Vol. 35, No. 3 (Mar., 1920), pp. 129-136</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.cite-automate.fr">conservation of automata</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2011/07/123_years_later_voice_of_thoma.html">Thomas Edison's talking doll</a></li>
